overview: Presenting 69 of our most unforgettable classic scenes with the hottest, legendary Vivid babes of the '90s! Jenna! Janine! Christy! Kobe! Julia Ann! Ashlyn! Nikki Dial! Tiffany! Raylene! Jill! Heather! Celeste! Jeanna! Asia! You name her, she's here in this special edition gift to all our loyal fans. If you only buy one DVD this year, make it 69 Scenes!
title: 69 Scenes: Superstars of the 90's
